   <lg xml:id="PN2">
<l><pb facs="2" n="2"/><lb n="12" />maṇṭiṇinta nilaṉum</l>
<l><pb facs="3" n="3"/><lb n="1" />nilaṉēntiya vicumpum</l>
<l>vicumputaivaru vaḷiyum</l>
<l>vaḷittalaiiya tīyun</l>
<l>tī<gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> nīrumeṉṟāṅ</l>
<l>kaim<lb n="2" />perum pūtat tiyaṟkai pōlap</l>
<l>pōṟṟārp pōṟuttaluñ cūḻcciyat talamum</l>
<l><gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>n te<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>lu maḷiyu muṭai<lb n="3" />yōy</l>
<l>niṉkaṭaṟ piṟanta ñāyiṟu peyarttuniṉ</l>
<l>veṇṭalaip puṇarik kuṭakaṭa<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> kuḷikkum</l>
<l>yāṇar vaippi ṉaṉṉāṭ<lb n="4" />ṭup poruna</l>
<l>vāṉa varampaṉai nīyō peruma</l>
<l>valaṅkuḻaip puravi yaivaroṭu ciṉaiiya</l>
<l>nilantalaik koṇṭa<lb n="5" /> polampūn tumpai</l>
<l>yīraim patiṉmarum porutukaḷat toḻiyap</l>
<l>peruñcōṟṟu mikupatam varai<lb n="6" />yātu koṭuttōy</l>
<l>pāalpuḷippiṉum pakaliruḷiṉu</l>
<l><gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>vēta neṟitiriyiṉun</l>
<l>tiriyāc<lb n="7" /> cuṟṟamoṭu muḻutucēṇ viḷaṅka</l>
<l>naṭukkiṉṟi niliyarō vattai yaṭukkattuc</l>
<l>ciṟutalai nav<lb n="8" />vip peruṅkaṇ māppiṇai</l>
<l>yanti yantaṇa raruṅkaṭa ṉiṟu‡ku</l>
<l>muttī viḷakkiṟ ṟuñcum</l>
<l>poṟ<lb n="9" />kōṭ ṭimaiyamum potiyamum pōṉṟē</l>
         </lg>
   <p xml:id="PN2-intro">
tiṇai pāṭāṇṭiṇai tuṟai vāḻttiyal – cēramāṉpe<lb n="10" />ruñcōṟṟutiyañ cōlātaṉai murañci<gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> muṭinākarāyar-  
</p>
   <p xml:id="PN246-comm">
aṇucceṟinta nilaṉu mannilatti ṉōṅki
<lb n="11" />ya vākāyamu mavvāka<gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/>tait taṭavivaruṅ kāṟṟu makkāṟṟiṉkaṭ ṭaṟuppaṭṭa tīyu mattīyōṭu
<lb n="12" /> māṟupaṭṭa nī<gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/>rumeṉa vaivakaippaṭṭa periya pūtattiṉatu taṉmaipōla<gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/>kaiva‡ piḻaiceytāl
<pb facs="4" n="4"/><lb n="1" /> piḻaiyaip poṟutta<gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/>ḻa poṟukkumaḷavalla<gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> maḻittaṟ<gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/>cā<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> mucāviṉataka
<lb n="2" />lamu mavarai yaḻittaṟkēṟṟa maṉavaliyuñ cāturaṅkavaliyu mavvāṟṟā <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>varai <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ḻittalu mavar vaḻipaṭṭā
<lb n="3" /> lavarkkuc ceyyu maruḷumuṭaiyōy - niṉatu kaṭaṟṟōṉṟiya ñāyiṟu piṉṉu niṉatu veḷiya talaiporuntiya tirai
<lb n="4" />yaiyuṭaiya mēlkaṭaṟkaṇṇē mūḻkum putuvaruvā yiṭaiyaṟāta vūrkaḷaiyumuṭaiya nalla nāṭṭiṟku vēntē
<lb n="5" /> vāṉavarampaṉī peruma - vākalā lacainta talaiyāṭṭamaṇinta kutiraiyaiyuṭaiya pāṇṭava raivaruṭaṉē ci
<lb n="6" />ṉattu nilattait tammiṭattē koṇṭa poṟpūntum paiyaiyuṭaiya turiyōtaṉaṉ mutalā
<lb n="7" />kiya nūṟṟuvarum pōrkkaḷattiṉkaṭ paṭuntuṇaiyum peruñ cōṟākiya mikka vuṇavai yirupaṭai
<lb n="8" />kkum varaiyātu vaḻaṅkiṉōy - pāl taṉiṉimaiyoḻintu puḷippiṉu ñāyiṟu taṉ viḷakkamoḻi
<lb n="9" />ntiruḷiṉu nāṉkuvētattiṉa toḻukkam vēṟupaṭiṉu vēṟupāṭillāta cūḻcciyaiyuṭaiya mantiric
<lb n="10" /> cuṟṟattō ṭoḻiyātu neṭuṅkālam viḷaṅkit tuḷakkamiṉṟi niṟpāyāka - varaimalaiyiṉkaṭ ciṟiya talai
<lb n="11" />yaiyuṭaiya maṟikaḷaiyuṭaiyavākiya periya kaṇṇaiyuṭaiya māṉpiṇaika ḷantikkālattē yantaṇar ceytaṟkari
<lb n="12" />ya kaṭaṉākiya vāvutiyaip paṇṇu muttīyākiya viḷakkiṉkaṇṇē tuyilum poṟcikaraṅkaḷaiyuṭaiya vimaiya
<pb facs="5" n="5"/><lb n="1" />malaiyum potiyiṉmalaiyum pōṉṟeṉṟavāṟu - kuḷikkunāṭeṉa viyaiyum - kuḷikkunāṭeṉa viṭattu
<lb n="2" /> nikaḻ poruḷiṉ ṟoḻiliṭattumē lēṟiniṉṟatu – aṉṟi yitaṉai viṉāvākki ñāyiṟu kuḷikkumeṉpataṉai mu<gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/><g rend="vowel-sign">i</g>
<lb n="3" /> yataṉai yavviṉāviṟkup poruḷākki yuraippārumuḷar - muttīyāvaṉa - ākavanīyaṅ kārukapattiyan teṉ
<lb n="4" />ṟicaiyaṅki - āṅku mattaiyu macainilai - aikāra muṉṉilai viḷakkiniṉṟatu - nilantalaikkoṇṭa veṉpataṟku
<lb n="5" /> nilaṅkōṭal kāraṇamākac cūṭiyaveṉi ṉummaiyum - pōṟṟārppoṟuttaṉ mutalākiya
<lb n="6" /> kuṇaṅkaḷaiyuṭaiyōy poruna varaiyātukoṭuttōy vāṉavarampaṉai peruma nī puḷi
<lb n="7" />ppiṉu miruḷiṉun tiriyiṉu mamaiyamum potiyiṉum pōṉṟu naṭukkiṉṟic cuṟṟamoṭu viḷaṅ
<lb n="8" />ki niṟpāyākaveṉak kūṭṭi viṉaimuṭivu ceyka - pōṟṟārppoṟuttaṉ mutalākiya kuṇaṅkaḷai yaraciyala
<lb n="9" />ṭaivāṟ kūṟukiṉṟārātaliṟ pūtaṅkaḷi ṉaṭaivu kūṟārāyiṉār - itaṉāṟ colliyatu niṉkaṭaṟpiṟantañāyiṟu
<lb n="10" /> niṉkaṭaṟkuḷikku nāṭaṉātalāṟ celvamuṭaiyai yākaveṉṟu vāḻttavē<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>ṭuvatiṉmaiyi ṉīṭu vāḻkaveṉa vā
<lb n="11" />ḻttiyavāṟāyiṟṟu-2-

         </p>
